{"data":[{"date":"17:07 17/07","title":"M\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb C\u0110V ch\u00ea x\u1ea5u","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/mau-ao-dau-mua-giai-201819-cua-mu-bi-cdv-che-xau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong video m\u1edbi b\u1ecb r\u00f2 r\u1ec9, MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu \u00e1o s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong clip, Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n MU gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf d\u00f9ng cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1eabu \u00e1o MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 b\u1ecb C\u0110V ch\u00ea x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1eabu \u00e1o MU m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 b\u1ecb C\u0110V ch\u00ea x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/kit_1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mata trong clip nh\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a MU.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, trang ch\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Man United s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng clip hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi. Khi MU ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u00e3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i clip k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng x\u00f3a \u0111i ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ecdc tr\u1eafng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u1edf vai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c s\u1ecdc \u0111en. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u1eabu \u00e1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb ngang song song \u1edf b\u1ee5ng \u00e1o. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ray t\u00e0u h\u1ecfa. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1edfi Newton Heath - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ec1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man United b\u00e2y gi\u1edd - xu\u1ea5t th\u00e2n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft t\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng Lancashire v\u00e0 Yorkshire.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n k\u1ebb ngang m\u00e0u \u0111en \u1edf b\u1ee5ng, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qu\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU c\u0169ng s\u1ebd mang m\u00e0u \u0111en. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng khi MU lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n m\u1eb7c qu\u1ea7n tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 m\u1eb7c qu\u1ea7n \u0111en khi ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ea7n s\u00e1ng m\u00e0u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung duong ke den - net moi trong trang phuc san nha cua MU.\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb \u0111en - n\u00e9t m\u1edbi trong trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/kit3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb \u0111en - n\u00e9t m\u1edbi trong trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgay sau khi m\u1eabu \u00e1o m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a MU b\u1ecb ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, fan \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ch\u00ea bai trang ph\u1ee5c n\u00e0y. Tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: \"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a n\u1ed5i trang ph\u1ee5c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU. Tr\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb ngang tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7\".<br />\r\n<br />\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Jonas Lyngdam \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"\u00c1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a MU s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb m\u00e0u \u0111en kia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng. Nh\u00ecn m\u00e0u \u0111en v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eb3ng \u0103n kh\u1edbp t\u00ed n\u00e0o\". T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n David Corby c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y MU ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc qu\u1ea7n m\u00e0u \u0111en.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4305","checkdouble":"191449"},{"date":"14:08 17/07","title":"VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng 17/7, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi v\u0103n b\u1ea3n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a VFF ghi r\u00f5 c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi 3/9/2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 16 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi HAGL \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0: V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n S\u01a1n, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 8 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i bao g\u1ed3m 6 ng\u00f4i sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0&nbsp;\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Th\u00e0nh Chung, Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng hai ng\u00f4i sao qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng) hay b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f9ng t\u00ean B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp d\u00f9 anh n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 26 tu\u1ed5i. Do m\u1ed7i \u0110T Olympic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 nh\u01b0 \u0110inh Thanh Trung hay Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi v\u00f2ng 20 V-League kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, hai chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-giai-tu-hung-vff-2018-279-191323.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-giai-tu-hung-vff-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-giai-tu-hung-vff-2018-279-191323.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng VFF 2018</span><br>\r\nBongda24h.vn c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf VFF 2018 C\u00fap Vinaphone di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3-7/8 t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4304","checkdouble":"191430"},{"date":"14:47 17/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00f3t hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</h2><h2>AFC mu\u1ed1n&nbsp;b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 g\u1ed3m Hong Kong, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0i Loan, trong khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam nam chung bang voi Nhat Ban tai ASIAD 2018.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 UAE v\u00e0 Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y sau khi 2 qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i l\u00ean Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 - AFC v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u00f3m 4 khi ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i, tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf Indonesia \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 cho UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Erick Thohir - Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch&nbsp;\u1ee6y ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD Indonesia chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;AFC mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu Palestine v\u00e0 UAE mu\u1ed1n tham d\u1ef1, ch\u1ec9 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. AFC r\u1ea5t d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c t\u1eeb trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA)&nbsp;cho hay k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng v\u00ec sai s\u00f3t tr\u00ean m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c chia b\u1ea3ng h\u00f4m 5/7 v\u1eeba qua ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi OCA v\u00e0 AFC \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\">VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4303","checkdouble":"191435"},{"date":"16:21 17/07","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang theo 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i 23. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 17 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Miura khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mang theo 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t bao g\u1ed3m 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, 7 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, 7 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n h\u1ebft t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd sang Indonesia c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n cho m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/24/Thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-du-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i \u0111i 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb hai CLB c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u1ea5t V-League hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Duy M\u1ea1nh, Th\u00e0nh Chung v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 6 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, H\u1ed3ng Duy, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 V\u0103n S\u01a1n v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. V\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1eabn HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. V\u00e0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i sinh ng\u00e0y 26/5/1995. Anh cao 1m76, n\u1eb7ng 69kg v\u00e0 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 15 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trinh Van Loi\" title=\"Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/hi-phong-clb-tphcm-vong-21-vleague-2017_1w6rybg36rtj01fp39bd780xmb.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u1edbp n\u0103ng khi\u1ebfu HAGL v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n L\u1ea1ch Tray theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 cao 1m65 nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao khu trung tuy\u1ebfn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, Th\u00e0nh Long c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng. Anh ra s\u00e2n 14 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea3 V\u0103n L\u1ee3i v\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh Long \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong s\u1ed1 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00fang 3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh 18 tr\u1eadn/19 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean BXH. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Nguyen Anh Duc ghi ban vao luoi Jordan\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Jordan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nguyen-anh-duc-hay-cu-phieu-khi-doi-chan-con-cho-phep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 su\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u2018kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t\u2019 gi\u1eefa Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 trung phong h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan, kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c c\u00f2n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bai-toan-hau-u23-viet-nam-lam-sao-de-giu-lua-toi-asiad-168-179252.html\">B\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u1eadu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1eeda t\u1edbi Asiad?</span><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a qua, th\u00ec li\u1ec7u nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4302","checkdouble":"191444"},{"date":"17:22 17/07","title":"Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min c\u00f3\u00a0t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Tottenham t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 52 tr\u1eadn cho Spurs, v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-min c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Son Heung-min c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/liverpool-muon-vuot-mat-mu-va-tottenham-vu-ronaldo-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Son Heung-Min g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Spurs tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham gia ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi nam gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Son Heung-min, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ec7n\u2019Jo Hyeon-woo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n s\u1ebd th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m HCV tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng sau. G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Uijo (Gamba Osaka). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\">VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp 30 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:\n115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4301","checkdouble":"191451"},{"date":"15:48 17/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tham gia World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang du l\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThibaut Courtois m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao g\u1ea7n 2m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Ri\u00eang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Courtois nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Courtois tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng h\u1ed5i. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng b\u0103ng. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1i \u201c\u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ttrong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi Courtois mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn 300 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n th\u00ec Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u00f3 2/3 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ee9c 200 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch, sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Courtois \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u201cv\u00f2i v\u0129nh\u201d Chelsea r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u0103ng m\u1ee9c thu nh\u1eadp m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Courtois \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Tenerife, T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a OndaCero, Courtois quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Courtois\" title=\"thu mon Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb l\u00e2u, Real \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32. Sau khi Man United d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 David De Gea, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Courtois kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real. Hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi con c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111ang sinh s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Madrid v\u00e0 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u anh \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Courtois t\u1eebng c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft cho Atletico d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard-172-191432.html\">Mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\">Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191416.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-bo-cuoc-vu-mateo-kovacic-172-191406.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4300","checkdouble":"191438"},{"date":"16:44 17/07","title":"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u, Hart \u201cmu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t\u201d sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Daily Mail g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1edfi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hart ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man City, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Joe Hart ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Torino v\u00e0 West Ham m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Hart t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHart th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i West Ham trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. C\u1ea3 Torino v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i. Anh bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City nh\u01b0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1nh m\u1eaft t\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/19/Joe-Hart-sang-My-du-dau-cung-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hart th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Torino v\u00e0 West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hart v\u1edbi Man xanh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Guardiola tin d\u00f9ng. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Shrewsbury Town nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/ n\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Joe Hart ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Citizens tham d\u1ef1 International Champions Cup t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. \u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Hart m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Man City sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart sap roi Man City lan nua.\" title=\"Joe Hart s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/17/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111i v\u1edbi Joe Hart sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Phil Foden. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Anh d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ebfn Chicago cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Foden \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111i M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Jorginho. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f9ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Maurizio Sarri. Man City c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Mateo Kovacic song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/Man-City-tu-choi-dua-Mateo-Kovacic-roi-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\">Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi-421-191068.html\">V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\">Man City CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toi-luot-man-city-vao-cuoc-vu-hang-hot-world-cup-2018-172-190594.html\">T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-man-city-172-190593.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4299","checkdouble":"191439"},{"date":"16:25 17/07","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13.7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Xherdan Shaqiri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 anh mong \u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 r\u1eddi Bayern Munich anh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb The Kop \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a&nbsp;m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Liverpool-mua-thanh-cong-Xherdan-Shaqiri-Ai-vui-ai-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Shaqiri h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 3 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City, Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Liverpool v\u00e0 HLV Klopp. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 13.7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 t\u1eeb Stoke City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb nh\u1ecf, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u00fap Liverpool gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m 3 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Shaqiri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Stoke City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stoke kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 l\u00e0 gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stoke khong the giu chan Shaqiri\" title=\"Stoke kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Shaqiri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/stoke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stoke kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Shaqiri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Stoke City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ghi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh anh g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 43% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Stoke \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nShaqiri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Stoke, anh chi\u1ebfm 50% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Shaqiri ra \u0111i, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Stoke s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Shaqiri, Swansea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Lukasz Fabianski v\u00e0o tay West Ham, trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bet365, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 - Vladimir Petkovic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Xherdan Shaqiri l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u1edf Euro 2016 v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic rat mung khi Shaqiri cap ben Liverpool\" title=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng khi Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/161852-hlv.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Vladimir Petkovic r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng khi Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u00e0y Shaqiri \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool, anh h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, Shaqiri s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Ngo\u00e0i ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Liverpool c\u0169ng gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i&nbsp;thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Vladimir Petkovic c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool, b\u1edfi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Kop kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Shaqiri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi. Khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, Shaqiri s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c The Kop ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Co hoi ra san cua Solanke o mua giai toi giam di dang ke\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Solanke \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/solonke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Solanke \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb b\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Dominic Solanke, Rhian Brewster v\u00e0 Ben Woodburn kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c \u00e9p gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u bu\u1ed9c Klopp ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, nh\u1eefng Solanke, Brewster v\u00e0 Woodburn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u&nbsp;h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Mohamed Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Philippe Coutinho r\u1eddi Liverpool c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca, Mohammed Salah tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah\" title=\"Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Salah-va-viec-gia-han-hop-dong--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng khi Liverpool mua Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng&nbsp;Anh v\u00e0 Champions League b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quan tr\u1ecdng, Klopp kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 Salah ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a t\u1edbi, g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho Salah s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt khi Shaqiri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anfield. HLV Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Shaqiri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Salah trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Shaqiri, Salah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Moses Simon</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Moses Simon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho KAA Gent \u1edf B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Shaqiri, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Moses Simon khong con co hoi toi Liverpool\" title=\"Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/simnon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n3 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o KAA Gent, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ghi 21 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 108 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-xherdan-shaqiri-172-191137.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Moses Simon kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4298","checkdouble":"191445"},{"date":"17:39 17/07","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/alex-sandro-dong-y-sang-psg-thay-vi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec M.U. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t sao h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus su\u1ed1t 1 n\u0103m qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlex Sandro n\u1ed5i l\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Porto v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus. 3 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. \u1ede Sandro s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i luy\u1ec7n trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Alex Sandro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u201cb\u1eaft ch\u1ebft\u201d b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1ecdc bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Alex-Sandro-dong-y-sang-PSG-thay-vi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Shaw kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. HLV Jose Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Ashley Young \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 33 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. M.U c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus m\u1edbi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh (112 tri\u1ec7u Euro). Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u00e0 Alex Sandro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Sandro cua Juventus\" title=\"Alex Sandro cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-177,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd sang PSG thay v\u00ec M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb The Sun, Sandro mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi PSG nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 M.U. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ch\u1ed7 cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, M.U s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1n Shaw v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Club America, San Jose Earthquakes, AC Milan, Liverpool v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Bayern Munich t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-92-trieu-bang-cho-bo-doi-croatia-172-191421.html\">M.U chi 92 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-muon-vuot-mat-mu-vu-danny-rose-172-191408.html\">PSG mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Tottenham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ivan-perisic-noi-gi-truoc-loi-moi-goi-toi-mu-cua-mourinho-172-191400.html\">Ivan Perisic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1edbi M.U c\u1ee7a Mourinho?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-chi-ra-mu-can-chieu-mo-ngay-sao-bu-dt-croatia-421-191381.html\">3 l\u00fd do ch\u1ec9 ra M.U c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay sao b\u1ef1 \u0110T Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\">99% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4297","checkdouble":"191446"},{"date":"17:49 17/07","title":"Kante   Jorginho   ???: 5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/5-ung-vien-cho-vi-tri-con-lai-noi-hang-tien-ve-chelsea.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Napoli. Chelsea mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kante l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues. V\u1eady c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi?\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ai xung dang tien ten vao vi tri con lai noi hang tien ve 3 nguoi cua Chelsea?\" title=\"Ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/5-ung-vien-cho-vi-tri-con-lai-noi-hang-tien-ve-chelsea.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ai x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCesc Fabregas</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,48</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 3,51</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf Stamford Bridge \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.&nbsp;V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Jorginho</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kante l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a The Blues.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Sarri s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i Chelsea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Sarri s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i Chelsea nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Chelsea-mua-Jorginho-Sarri-se-thay-doi-Chelsea-nhu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Jorginho \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eb1m cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa khi c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. Cesc Fabregas ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea. F4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Maurizio Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 3,51 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat, anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 1,48 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00fat xa t\u1ed1t, F4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Fabregas t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kh\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ross Barkley</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,37</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,37</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoss Barkley chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay t\u1eeb Everton v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo&nbsp;khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co man ra mat khong thanh cong\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/25/conte-noi-gi-ve-su-mo-nhat-cua-ross-barkley.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 131 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ef1u sao Everton kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Barkley \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, Barkley ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Sarri d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barkley t\u1ea1i Everton (2015/16) anh ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Goodison Park ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu 8 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoss Barkley s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, Barkley ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,54</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,25</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" title=\"tien ve Ruben Loftus-Cheek\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/10/sao-tre-chelsea-toi-crystal-palace-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ruben Loftus-Cheek nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLoftus-Cheek th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, nh\u01b0ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m Loftus-Cheek \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Aleksandr Golovin</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2,2</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,6</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 5</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 11m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><br>\r\n            <img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Golovin\" title=\"Alex Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/chelsea-gap-doi-thu-o-thuong-vu-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA, anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Nga, \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Golovin v\u1ec1 The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA v\u00e0 \u0110T Nga, Golovin th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u01a1i sau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, song v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u00f3 trung b\u00ecnh 1,9 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra 1,6 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat, anh c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nga.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 2,9</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 1,6</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua: 11</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo Corriere dello Sport, Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Chelsea-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-cua-Lazio-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 2,9 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Hamsik (3,2), ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Napoli \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Lazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4296","checkdouble":"191452"},{"date":"09:32 17/07","title":"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/cau-chuyen-xuc-dong-ve-tam-op-chan-cua-pogba-tai-world-cup-2018.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Paul Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef trong tay t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, n\u01a1i in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 y\u00eau d\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh qua \u0111\u1eddi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap-c197-p1.html\" title=\"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p\" type=\"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p\"> b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p</span>, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00f2 m\u00f2 khi lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhiniki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n, t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in h\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 Fassou Antoine c\u1ee7a Pogba, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 79.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pogba t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/DiLKd05XUAUMygZjpglarge.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Pogba lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n trong tay khi \u0111ang \u00f4m chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Fassou l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Guinea, sau \u0111\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi sinh s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, n\u01a1i con trai \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia x\u1ee9 s\u1edf l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a cha, tr\u00ean t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Ph\u00e1p: &quot;\u00d4i Ch\u00faa, \u0111\u1eebng tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t con v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c n\u00f3i. H\u00e3y tha th\u1ee9 cho con v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 hay bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 h\u00e3y gi\u00fap con tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd ngh\u0129&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1eb5m tr\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong tay, Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y t\u1eb7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9 th\u00e2n y\u00eau v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha qu\u00e1 c\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Pogba c\u0169ng ch\u1ee5p m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh khi c\u1ea7m tr\u00ean tay chi\u1ebfc \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Manchester United ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng ch\u00fa th\u00edch: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a B\u1ed1. B\u1ed1 \u01a1i c\u00e1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho b\u1ed1&quot;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba chia se tren Twitter buc hinh chup cung voi tam op chan in hinh bo.\" title=\"Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n in h\u00ecnh b\u1ed1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Screen_Shot_20180717_at_033124.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Pogba chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m \u1ed1p ch\u00e2n in h\u00ecnh b\u1ed1.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u1ec9 2 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u00f4ng Fassou qua \u0111\u1eddi, Pogba t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c sinh nh\u1eadt l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 79 cho b\u1ed1 ngay t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n. Trong t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p hai cha con b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh sinh nh\u1eadt, Pogba chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng b\u1ed1 th\u00e2n y\u00eau, con t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 con c\u1ee7a b\u1ed1&quot;. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, t\u00ecnh y\u00eau m\u00e0 Pogba d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea5ng th\u00e2n sinh l\u00e0 v\u00f4 b\u1edd b\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m nay, khi ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, Pogba g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ed1 n\u01a1i thi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0ng qua nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o ph\u00f4ng m\u1eb7c b\u00ean trong: &quot;Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt b\u1ed1, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n d\u00f5i theo con v\u00e0 c\u00e1c anh em&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, Pogba chia s\u1ebb: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 90 ph\u00fat ngo\u00e0i kia \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u1eefng trang s\u1eed c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c&quot;, Pogba chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u1eefng trang m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4295","checkdouble":"191415"},{"date":"09:12 17/07","title":"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi Milan l\u00e0\u2026 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha cho r\u1eb1ng AC Milan n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Milan trong suy tho\u00e1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Italia, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2012/13 t\u1edbi nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u1ec9 sau Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Milan ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 b\u00e1n CLB cho c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 mua s\u1eafm r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9, Rossoneri v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-la-tich-cuc-cho-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c chi ti\u00eau qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Milan vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a UEFA. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecb c\u01a1 quan quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" title=\"bong da chau au\" type=\"bong da chau au\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span> c\u1ea5m d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong v\u00f2ng 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNi\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Milan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Serie A trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Bianconeri m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" title=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1c quan cho Milan. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua 7 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n San Siro tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean cho m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng t\u0103m t\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Juventus k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo&rdquo;, Kaka n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Omnisport. &ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 cho Milan. Ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y khi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia-c176-p1.html\" title=\"Bong da y\" type=\"Bong da y\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia</span> \u0111ang d\u00e2ng cao. Cristiano Ronaldo mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. C\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson-180-191170.html\">Roma b\u00e1o tin vui cho Real v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4294","checkdouble":"191405"},{"date":"11:16 17/07","title":"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo: Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e1m b\u1ecf t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u1ec9 cho m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng hoan ngh\u00eanh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Champions League \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, trong \u0111\u00eam Turin \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 4 v\u1eeba qua, <em>si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa &ldquo;xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u1ed5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a anh <u>nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</u>. Trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc phi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nhen nh\u00f3m trong \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Allianz. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, 3 th\u00e1ng sau, h\u1ecd <strong>bi\u1ebfn m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</strong>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, <em>h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Ronaldo &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh 5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</em> v\u00e0 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo Khi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-Khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gi\u00e0nh v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 danh hi\u1ec7u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Juventus, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ronaldo h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 khi <u>c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi m\u1edf ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Juve kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1</u>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t cho nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bianconeri c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y</span> t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t ph\u00e9p t\u00ednh: Ronaldo 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro? Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, <em>nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111ang k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi v\u00f4 t\u1eadn</em>. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o l\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00f4ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Ronaldo? Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n? Ronaldo c\u00f3 c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9?&nbsp; Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 sao? Juventus c\u00f3 l\u00e2m v\u00e0o ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n? C\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia? v.v. v\u00e0 v.v.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo roi Real mang theo nhieu danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-roi-Real-mang-theo-nhieu-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CR7 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKhi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn: Cho t\u1edbi <u>tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi Real, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1</u> c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u01a1i r\u1ed9ng, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng <em>Serie A l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng</em>. Nh\u1eefng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Francesco Totti v\u00e0 Javier Zanetti c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i 40. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, Fabio Quagliarella d\u00f9 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 19 b\u00e0n sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" title=\"Juventus chieu mo Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/juventus-chieu-mo-ronaldo-khi-cuoc-song-buoc-phai-co-kich-tinh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 l\u00fd khi Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi Juventus th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng con s\u1ed1 55 b\u00e0n sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 Higuain ghi cho Juve t\u1edbi nay l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o (trung b\u00ecnh 0,52 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 Ronaldo, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ec3 s\u1ee3. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Bianconeri m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Emre Can.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro,...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn tham v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Serie A, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Ronaldo. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i n\u00e0y 7 n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 d\u00f9 \u00edt d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an nh\u00e0n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m n\u00e2ng cao Scudetto v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f4i khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. <strong>Juventus mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i vinh quang t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</strong>, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 12 n\u0103m. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 l\u1ea7n trong 4 m\u00f9a qua nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 Barcelona v\u00e0 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tong hop: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (Vong 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Inter Milan 2-3 Juventus (V\u00f2ng 35 Serie A 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/tong-hop-inter-milan-23-juventus-vong-35-serie-a-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 Champions League sau 12 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh Real v\u00e0 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb penalty ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 do ch\u00ednh Ronaldo th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Champions League, Juve ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb CR7 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng vua \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Real Madrid, l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed3i. Real \u0111\u00e3 3 n\u0103m li\u1ec1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League (4 l\u1ea7n sau 5 n\u0103m) v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo &ndash; ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 coi nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Ronaldo-toi-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Allianz</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Juventus mang v\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi PSG ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Neymar. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil mang l\u1ea1i cho PSG th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus th\u1ea5y r\u00f5. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu cao \u0111\u1ec3 CLB m\u1edf k\u00e9t tr\u1ea3 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/juventus-ban-520-nghin-ao-dau-du-cristiano-ronaldo-con-chua-ra-mat-465-191382.html\" target=\"_blank\">l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n ra c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t b\u00e1u v\u1eadt t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Turin. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng sau 4 n\u0103m, CR7 th\u00f4ng qua th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rat nhieu CDV Juventus chao don su xuat hien cua Ronaldo.\" title=\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Juventus ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/FBL-ITA-SERIEA-JUVENTUS-RONALDO-(2).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u0110V Juventus nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a CR7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: Tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Juventus n\u0103m qua v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 doanh thu b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Inter Milan b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1n c\u00e2n n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Juve \u0111ang t\u0103ng l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng v\u00e0 &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hoan ngh\u00eanh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 (c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League), vi\u1ec7c Juve l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m (mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus-184-191410.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/hanh-dong-thu-vi-cua-ronaldo-khi-gioi-thieu-ao-dau-tai-juventus-327-191392.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sao-juventus-noi-gi-ve-dong-doi-tan-binh-ronaldo-176-191387.html\">Sao Juventus n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00e2n binh Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4293","checkdouble":"191424"}]}